  "prompt": "I'm new to Quora. What does it mean when someone says they are following me?",
  "response": "Welcome to Quora! When someone follows you on the platform, it means they are interested in your activity and want to keep up with your contributions. This could include the questions you ask, the answers you provide, and the other content you share. Essentially, they will receive updates or notifications about your activity, which allows them to engage with your thoughts and insights on the topics you discuss. It\u2019s a way to build a community and foster discussions around shared interests.",
